title: Rabbit
subtitle: They can hop, and they are delicious.
desc1: Rabbits can be eaten. This information might seem foreign to you, but rabbits (Leporidae) are very common as food in some parts of Europe, and the US. It is also considered as a delicacy in France.
desc2: It is rich in nutrients, hence it is not strange why this is such a common food in those areas. Also, they can die of fright easily. Try not to scare them at pet shops.
